Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the place that the\nmonk spoke of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A hair cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:57.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:11.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?\NWhen I die, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:14.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:23.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I died hating you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And at that moment,\nmy soul became immobile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you live,\NI cannot be saved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Kikyo asleep?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She seems a bit sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were able to break through\nmy barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was there anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the one who has been\nluring women's souls away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If so, please let them return!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha set out to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... Inuyasha is trying to\ncome here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you to Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body...can't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-that's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons who were gathering\nthe dead souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo is behind this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo, is it really you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's here to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't allow any interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't still mean to\nkill Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:36.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone purposely set\nyou two at odds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It wasn't Inuyasha who killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You look as though you expect\nme to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who caused my death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that person dies,\nwill I be resurrected?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The dead wish for one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To live once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! A wish that cannot come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, the dead can wish for\none thing which can come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to steal his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,from the one I will never forgive\nif he dares to forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never forgive if\nhe forgets you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you mean Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wishes for my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:36.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means he has regrets about\nour fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Regret all he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:43.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall never let him forget... about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time will not go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:50.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I can exist is the time\nthat is frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:56.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will be able to continue\nliving in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:00.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even now, Inuyasha thinks\nabout you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha loves you!\NHe always has!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and I parted\ndespising each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The love you speak of is but\na shallow emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which only served to\ndeepen the hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:27.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing is stronger in strengthening\nresolve than bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he must love, then love\nmy consuming hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As for me, I will love his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which is about to fall\ninto deep despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Your hatred is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Talk to Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell her how Naraku deceived\nyou both!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:02.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha can't see me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it is you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who's been gathering\nthe souls of dead women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This body, molded from\nearth and bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:29.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,needs to be nourished with\nhuman souls, else I cannot move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... you must despise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Driven by my hatred towards you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:41.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have gathered the souls of the dead\nto remain in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may hate me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,never a day went by\nwithout my thinking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought{\i0} so... {\i1}Inuyasha has\nnever forgotten Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:12.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course! But I feel a bit sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's been taken from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, what am I saying?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's not my boyfriend\nor anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter what your appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would never hate you or\nthink less of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:40.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I were to kill you\nwith these hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! W-wait...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:55.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,after meeting you, I stopped\nbeing a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I became a mere woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is what I longed for\nwhen I was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... You're going to\naccept her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess... it's only to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What am I doing here anyway?\NI'm such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm starting to cry!?\NCripes... what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This nostalgic scent of her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:33.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only difference is that\nshe has no warmth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her body died...so it's cold...\nand sad...and lonely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We cannot return to that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I want to stay like this\na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I cannot do anything\nfor you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to stay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I wish time would stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all right?\NIf time would stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't care...\nif I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't watch this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't interfere, so release me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, are you two listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will never let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come with me to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's being dragged in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:37.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what're you doing?!\NYou must get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! He's unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo! You can hear me, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha said he wants to\nbe with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but he never said\nhe wanted to die with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unlike you, Inuyasha must go\nafter Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who tricked him fifty years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More than anything, Inuyasha wants\nto live to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is determined to avenge\nyour death as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:25.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:30.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will getting revenge bring\nthis body back to life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rather than live with\nmy memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:44.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and I have the same wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Inuyasha were conscious,\nhe would never follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get away from Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:58.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do... not... touch... Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's taking my souls once again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before this body is\ncompletely emptied...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Wake up, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:42.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome's voice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...is...here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ka...go...me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh!? What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me? Well... err...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that girl more dear to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, do not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My feeling when\nmy lips were against yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,do you think you can find\nthe Sacred Jewels alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... don't think I can help\nyou anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one who\ncan see the Jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course, you have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all you need me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:17.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a thing to say.\NSorry! Forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I'm alone\nin this strange world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm feeling Ionely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it.\NYou couldn't see me, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I did see it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From the start to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, please leave me alone\nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-hey! What's this about...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Start to finish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kagome! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Start to finish means\neverything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw everything!\NFrom a front row seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? You found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you seen Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've seen that pose before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must mean that\NKagome is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that Kagome is\nfull of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of your\nown sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:01.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since the day you fell\nfrom the cliff, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I am a dead woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I guess I still long for\nthis world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you still seek Inuyasha's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just met Inuyasha moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I barely missed killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me everything you know\nabout this Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My rotten spirit has some\nuse after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:49.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look good?\NDon't you want to devour me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want a body that moves freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to posses the Sacred Jewel...\nand Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And pass on power... to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:07.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything started from\nthe evil designs of Onigumo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:11.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He called forth the demons\nand was eaten by them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}thus was born the demon Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... That wild robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He used to say that\nthe Sacred Jewel grows in beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when it is tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:31.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He caused hatred between\nmyself and Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:35.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then stole the Jewel\nthat had been sullied.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister... Inuyasha was seriously\nwounded by Naraku again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:47.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just thought I should know the\ncircumstances of my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, Inuyasha has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His face had a softness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Back then, he trusted no one...\nhis eyes were cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is a strange child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:06.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She has been able to slowly\nheal Inuyasha's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl again... She's the one\nwho changed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:17.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had lived, I would have been\nthe one to heal his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:23.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sister... are you not able to\nbreak away from the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We shall meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long will you linger... Sister?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:22.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, Kagome wasn't her\nusual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what happened with Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What you always do with women...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:34.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You! You participated in such\nan act in front of Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya usually do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will Kagome come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She seemed to be\nquite troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never a day went by without\nmy thinking of you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spoke the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My feeling when my lips were\nagainst yours...was real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And my words were real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that girl more dear to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, what will you do, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo could not have gone far.\NWill you go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't Kagome more precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, hurry and make up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was in such a daze, I forgot\nall my things back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:31.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will you do, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who will you choose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't I choose both?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... two-timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it often happens\nwith men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:53.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, no matter what happens,\nshe must not find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If what you just said should\never leak out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it's sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:05.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It means divine punishment\nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poor Inuyasha... He wasn't\nbeing malicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We learn that a village nearby\nspecializes in demon extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:54.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe we can gain information about\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.35,0:23:57.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It turns out we are not the only ones\nwho thought along that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:24:00.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chain-Scythes attack the fellow\ndemon terminators!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The village under seize!\NA brother and a sister trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:07.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is everything arranged by... him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Enter Sango the Demon Slayer"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:13.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
